entries.s_30: It was horrible. I barely made it out alive.
entries.s_34: The...the people dying...the virus. They came back to eat us. Oh no.....I can still see them if I close my eyes. Make it go away.
entries.s_35: I can't wait until my shuttle arrives. I am not coming back to Dathomir ever.
